===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''egret''' (''plural'' '''egrets''')

# Any of various [[wading bird]]s of the genera ''[[Egretta]]'' or ''[[Ardea]]'' that includes [[heron]]s, many of which are white or buff, and several of which develop fine plumes during the breeding season. 

